name: Bae Suzy
description:
If you like my LoRAs please consider to support me by buying me a coffee here so I can make a new LoRA faster. I do open commissions there too if you want to make your own custom LoRA.

Bae Suzy v3 here

Don't forget to include trigger word: baesuzy

Best checkpoints/models to use:

Realistic: VisionGen, ChillOutMix, ArtEros, snapdd00, henrealmix

Fanart/painting style: Dreamshaper, LucidMix, SunshineMix, Majicmix

Use it wisely. I don't responsible for anything you generated with this LoRa.

Join KPOP Diffusion Discord: https://discord.gg/NrBDMX79Da

modelVersions.name: Bae Suzy - v1
modelVersions.description:
Trained on latest version of Linaqruf's colab using 30 images with Analog Diffusion as its base model.

Best at close-up, pose will be repetitive at some seeds and prompts because its dataset have many similar pose, but it can be solved with Controlnet, the face similarity will be decrease though.
